00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:14.170
in their pocket and access
to the world's information

00:00:14.170 --> 00:00:15.480
at their fingertips.

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:17.870
However, getting and interacting
with that information

00:00:17.870 --> 00:00:19.220
isn't always easy.

00:00:19.220 --> 00:00:24.750
So where did I put
that bar code scanner?

00:00:24.750 --> 00:00:26.860
