00:00:28.610 --> 00:00:30.992
However, if we believe
in Moore's law at all,

00:00:30.992 --> 00:00:32.450
we can project that
there are going

00:00:32.450 --> 00:00:35.820
to be millions of smart devices
in our homes, in our work,

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:37.360
and everywhere in between.

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:39.540
Accessing functionality
from these devices

00:00:39.540 --> 00:00:41.670
can be just like using the web.

00:00:41.670 --> 00:00:45.451
You just walk up, tap, and go.

00:00:45.451 --> 00:00:45.950
Cool.

00:00:45.950 --> 00:00:47.830
There's a show in
